data.name: labelAltConfigDesc.Text
data.value: This copies the files from the Alt directory including: AddOns.txt - Set the addons to be loaded chat-cache.txt - Setup the chat window(s) config-cache.wtf - Camera Angle, Nameplates, etc layout-local.txt -Recount(addon) window settings macros-cache.txt - Alt specific macros This sync page does the same thing as the Alt File Sync page but only updates the selected alts here and updates all of the alt files (can't choose which get updated).
